name: The Road #1
description:
The Road #1 is the beginning of an ongoing mini series based on the escapades of the past and future. 

Every image shot while driving.

Shot on - Nikon AF with Ektar 100 film somewhere between the Mojave Desert and Joshua Tree in October 2019. Un-edited and raw.

The Raven ~ shapeshifters, creators of light and known to draw secrets from the shadows ~

Poppi
